      <description><![CDATA[Roblox has published its EU Digital Services Act transparency report for 2025, covering content moderation activity for 1 January – 31 December. I owned end-to-end delivery — scoping data requirements against Article 15 obligations, building the cross-functional production workflow, and driving on-time publication.]]></description>
